WEBVTT

00:01.380 --> 00:05.320
Hey, Tommy, this isn't the way to Crenshaw.
嘿 汤米 回家不该走这条路啊

00:06.100 --> 00:11.940
There's an accident on the 10. We're taking the surface streets. - Uh-huh.
10号公路上有车祸 只好走地面道路了。 - 哦

00:25.180 --> 00:27.200
Why are we, uh?
我们怎么...

00:31.860 --> 00:33.460
Oh, my God.
哦 老天

00:33.460 --> 00:37.280
He's kept tabs on her. Just in case you decided to...
他一直在暗中照看她 等你哪天想…

00:37.280 --> 00:40.660
This was your idea, Tom? - No  -It was my idea.
这是你的主意嘛 汤姆？- 不是  - 这是我的主意

00:40.660 --> 00:45.080
I talked him into it. - Yeah, talked him into it.  - Hey. Wait a minute, Edward.
是我说服了他  - 是啊！ 是你说服了他。 - 嘿，等一下，Edward.

00:47.000 --> 00:49.300
Edward. What are you so afraid of?
爱德华 你干嘛那么害怕？

00:49.300 --> 00:54.400
Just because I told you my story does not invite you to be a part of it.
我只想告诉你一个故事 又没叫你在里面瞎掺和

00:54.400 --> 00:56.100
Oh. Like the lady in the bar?
哦 就像酒吧里的那姑娘？

00:56.100 --> 00:57.180
- That's different.
- 那是两码事

00:57.280 --> 00:58.200
Tell me how is it different.
怎么个两码事？

00:58.860 --> 01:00.200
Because it is!
- 就是两码事

01:00.200 --> 01:01.020
How is it different?
有什么区别？

01:01.140 --> 01:04.340
You have no fucking idea who I am!
我是个什么人 你根本没概念

01:04.820 --> 01:07.680
I built a billion-dollar business up from nothing!
我从白手起家到今天的亿万身价

01:07.880 --> 01:09.880
Presidents have asked my advice.
连总统都要征询我的看法

01:09.880 --> 01:14.000
I have dined with royalty and I'm supposed to make out like, what...
我和王室成员共进过晚餐， 难到还要让我理解像什么...

01:14.180 --> 01:16.840
this trip was supposed to mean something to me?
这趟旅行对我应该有些什么意义呀？

01:17.080 --> 01:19.700
Like it was gonna change me?
就好像，它能改变我的人生似的...

01:21.820 --> 01:27.980
How did you see it playing out, Carter? I knock on the door, she answers. She's surprised and angry...
你认为事情该怎么发展 卡特？我敲门 然后她开门…她先是很惊讶 然后开始发火…

01:27.980 --> 01:31.520
but I tell her how much I love her and miss her.
但我还要说 我有多么爱她多么想她

01:31.520 --> 01:37.900
And, "Oh. By the way, I'm gonna be dead soon... so I'm reaching out to you because I don't wanna die alone"?
哦对了 "顺便说一句 我马上要死了… 所以才来找你 我不想孤零零的死"？

01:37.980 --> 01:39.620
Everyone is afraid to die alone.
凡人都害怕孤零零的死去

01:39.620 --> 01:41.540
I'm not everyone!
我不是凡人

01:42.700 --> 01:47.720
This was supposed to be fun.
这次旅行本来应该很有趣

01:48.220 --> 01:50.480
That's all it ever was.
曾经是的 但现在全完了

01:50.480 --> 01:52.480

